{"tid":1459691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給予外國政要譴責香港政府的殘暴行為的時間","createTime":"2019-08-12T19:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:15:02.000Z","uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f695159f8c619e3a3c7920bf54f814dea625f3b","tid":1459691,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:10:01.000Z","msg":"美國參議院領袖Mitch McConnell 警告，美國絕不接受香港政府鎮壓香港示威者。McConnell先生直接用了自治（autonomy）一詞來形容香港的政治制度。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-usa-mcconnell/u-s-senate-leader-any-violent-crackdown-in-hong-kong-would-be-completely-unacceptable-idUSKCN1V21ES?fbclid=IwAR1cKWN_SIrIMQt7JE28H_tCwlP_-387s8Akd2paTLxfcMYo92cDO95TVXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-usa-mcconnell%2Fu-s-senate-leader-any-violent-crackdown-in-hong-kong-would-be-completely-unacceptable-idUSKCN1V21ES%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1cKWN_SIrIMQt7JE28H_tCwlP_-387s8Akd2paTLxfcMYo92cDO95TVXc&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=73664016\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-usa-mcconnell%2Fu-s-senate-leader-any-violent-crackdown-in-hong-kong-would-be-completely-unacceptable-idUSKCN1V21ES%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1cKWN_SIrIMQt7JE28H_tCwlP_-387s8Akd2paTLxfcMYo92cDO95TVXc&h=242613c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-usa-mcconnell/u-s-senate-leader-any-violent-crackdown-in-hong-kong-would-be-completely-unacceptable-idUSKCN1V21ES?fbclid=IwAR1cKWN_SIrIMQt7JE28H_tCwlP_-387s8Akd2paTLxfcMYo92cDO95TVXc</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：（接續策略帖文）我們暫停衝擊的時候，國際社會就找到安全的反應時間做事（safe reaction time-span）。目前<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共已經犯下最殘暴也是最明顯的人道罪行&mdash;&mdash;警察開槍射盲女性救護員的眼</span></span>，我們就在此暫停衝擊行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">轉做和平集會、展覽、宣傳，也請外國領事來監護我們的和平集會。</span><br />\n這是<span style=\"color: red;\">給予外國政要一個安全的反應時間</span>，令他們可以<span style=\"color: red;\">譴責香港政府的殘暴行為</span>。而因為我們已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暫停武力衝擊或武力抵抗，我們不會犯錯而令這些外國政要尷尬</span></span>，例如當外國政要譴責香港政府殘暴的時候，我們第二日就在衝擊場所傷殘了一位警察或打死一個黑社會，這會令外國政要非常之尷尬的。<br />\n我是進入了禪定狀態給大家行動意見的。<br />\n玩外交關係，是這樣玩。香港建國之後，我會退出政壇，但我會持續講授這些策略給香港新一代的外交官，玩死中國。<br />\n我是非常謹慎的人。各位要知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157330209717225&amp;id=589657224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157330209717225%26id%3D589657224&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=17452485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157330209717225&amp;id=589657224</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">813繼續塞爆機場！！ 癱瘓機場！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"87f0b64712a0ab8f53f5958db1bed1beec7efdf0","tid":1459691,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:11:36.000Z","msg":"謝謝老師指教"},{"pid":"a1390a9337134d943a87599498b3885d86d405a6","tid":1459691,"uid":260009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3eee4123a52e89c2f435c53195e516d4c95a6f","tid":1459691,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"813塞爆機場，癱瘓機場！！"},{"pid":"77bd65e4932067c78d2c0d7a17fa94879dab7606","tid":1459691,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"813塞爆機場，癱瘓機場！！"},{"pid":"bcdf27096d4634b9169cf148122f726df29b28c6","tid":1459691,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:14:09.000Z","msg":"813塞爆機場，癱瘓機場！！"},{"pid":"8ccce6516a579c6a6fbaaf9fdb60957bf77b746d","tid":1459691,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"